{"id": "1272099381423898676", "channel_id": "1272099381423898676", "type": 0, "author_id": "1222582796816744458", "author_name": "zhaoxing233", "author_bot": false, "content": "總結：由指令卡觸發的增加力量的命輪特效（書包）/覺醒特效（艾瑞卡覺醒）/刻印可以受到詩箋加成；護盾狂氣和治療類的覺醒特效和刻印都不受加成，並且治療護盾類的覺醒卡會錯誤顯示生效。達芙戴爾的千面有顯示錯誤、索蕾爾朱玉未受到加成\n\n達芙戴爾的千面幻象在效果選擇界面會正常受到詩箋加成，但印出來之後沒有顯示。實際打出時正常受到加成", "timestamp": "2024-08-11T07:48:46.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-11T10:20:36.175000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1272099381696270396", "filename": "Image_1723362427897.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21967, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1272099381423898676/1272099381696270396/Image_1723362427897.jpg?ex=69cc251f&is=69cad39f&hm=ce6d5c20448f02c113c12ddff88b434f0db500bcddaf5807173e92707231c434&"}, {"id": "1272099382010970136", "filename": "Image_1723362429871.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 37235, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1272099381423898676/1272099382010970136/Image_1723362429871.jpg?ex=69cc251f&is=69cad39f&hm=fd7af023e51b45a9fb198cf4c292fe5ed49707129134079328fa3dfe72e2a8fc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1272099381423898676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一些關於詩箋的句尾加成的試驗", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
